{"tid":2513704,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】起公路跌左部iphone 如有拾獲 重酬1000","createTime":"2021-05-02T17:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T22:20:00.000Z","uid":92645,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2057458f39f46c0ab7fbfac04b79a16bc78ab907","tid":2513704,"uid":92645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日返到屋企，發現部電話唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9秒9開find my iphone<br />\n之後，神奇既事就發生左⋯⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我部電話竟然係呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeRJ6zzGFcoSmNFqmARGFQAAmxCmjHFL75bmu8t3Qf5iv?filename=euVfU6S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeuVfU6S.jpg&h=488339ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再開開google map睇睇街景⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR2bYTK8z3Ctd1G9mgPn3Z1WjvGszFunB1sgykCg1LJup?filename=cZMiSUd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZMiSUd.png&h=5058cef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度正正係我今日返屋企，出完獅子山落斜果個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好問我點解會飛左部電話出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之有巴打絲打渣車經過見倒，又有辨法執得返既，重酬1000<br />\n<br />\n萬分感謝！！"},{"pid":"66c716874b0d9d5e5cc0f336386ba6574f9b4d79","tid":2513704,"uid":154702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"你一千蚊飛的落去執好過啦"},{"pid":"8304d8ebf35c2f132ffef12bfe15b1d81e5a46b0","tid":2513704,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit